	[Next]
	Hey, have you come across[BR]
	Point Swaps before?[BR]
	[Pause 10]They're pretty fascinating[BR]
	Items, to be sure.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Well in case you weren't in[BR]
	the know, if you cook an item[BR]
	with a Point Swap, it has a[BR]
	good chance of...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Boom! Transforming into the[BR]
	opposite Item of its type![BR]
	[Pause 10]I tried it on a Super Shroom[BR]
	when I wanted Maple Syrup.[BR]
