#message:16:019
{
	[Next]
	Have you gotten ahold of items[BR]
	named the Hustle Drink and the[BR]
	Repel Gel?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Depending on the order you[BR]
	use them in combat, the effects[BR]
	can be either catastrophic or[BR]
	exemplary.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Using a Hustle Drink on its[BR]
	own will let you move two more[BR]
	times that turn![BR]
	Isn't that great?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	If you were to Double Dip a[BR]
	Hustle Drink and then a Repel[BR]
	Gel, you can become invsible[BR]
	and get two actions next turn.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I recommend trying it out,[BR]
	[Pause 10]unless you don't have the Double[BR]
	Dip Badge.[BR]
	[Wait][Yield][End]
}

