	[Next]
	Have you tried mixing Cake Mix[BR]
	with a Shooting Star before?[BR]
	[Pause 10]It is said to yield wonderful[BR]
	results... something like that.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It really makes you wonder...[BR]
	[Pause 10]What do stars taste like?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Just be careful you're not[BR]
	eating a resident of [SaveColor][Color:09]Love[BR]
	Heaven[RestoreColor]. [Pause 12]That would be most[BR]
	awfully bad, of course![BR]
	[Wait][Yield][End]
}

#message:16:022
{
	[Next]
	My chronicle states that[BR]
	each of the areas you visited[BR]
	are based on the colours[BR]
	of the rainbow. [BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[SaveColor][Color:05]Yellow for the Koopa Region,[BR]
	[Pause 10][SaveColor][Color:08]purple for the Desert Region.[BR]
	[Pause 10][SaveColor][Color:03]green for Gusty Gulch,[BR]
	[Pause 10][SaveColor][Color:02]blue for Shy Guy's Toy Box,[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[SaveColor][Color:07]red for Loveydovey Island,[BR]
	[Pause 10][SaveColor][Color:01]aqua for Flower Land,[BR]
	[Pause 10][SaveColor][Color:0D]black for the Shiver region[color:00][BR]
	[Pause 10]and [SaveColor][Color:09]Pink for Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Pause 10][Color:0A]Huff... puff... and that's it.[BR]
	[Pause 10]It says each land is a trademark[BR]
	of that specific Love Deity's[BR]
	colour and personality.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I'm just glad the Love Deities[BR]
	are doing better now, and it's[BR]
	all thanks to your efforts,[BR]
	Mario. Way to go![BR]
	[Wait][Yield][End]
}

#message:16:023
{
	[Next]
	Just the other day, I was[BR]
	fortunate enough to read the[BR]
	most fascinating book.[BR]
	[Pause 10]This book said, and I quote...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Color 0x00]"...the Evil King chortles, and[BR]
	a sacred rod and seven lights [BR]
	fade into darkness. A lovely [BR]
	maiden rises to the heavens.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	"But lo! A hero clad in red[BR]
	appears and travels the world.[BR]
	He gathers around him eight[BR]
	who are pure of heart.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	"This hero restores the seven[BR]
	lights, and they raise him high [BR]
	into the sky.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	"On the airy heights, the hero[BR]
	clashes with the Evil King.[BR]
	The lovely maiden wishes..."[BR]
	[Color 0x0A][Wait][Next]
	That's how it ended![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Somebody had torn out the rest[BR]
	of the pages! Now I'll never[BR]
	know the ending! What kind of[BR]
	no-good tears up books!?![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I think I have heard of this kind[BR]
	of story but I'm not sure where[BR]
	I read it...[BR]
	[Wait][Yield][End]
}

